  "title": "AI Fraud in Focus: Detecting and Defending",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">AI Fraud in Focus: Detecting and Defending <br/>Against Digital Deception in Insurance</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Explore how AI is transforming the landscape of insurance fraud. From deepfakes to synthetic identities, discover the tactics fraudsters use, the vulnerabilities they target, and the tools available to detect and prevent these threats. Gain actionable insights to strengthen defenses, safeguard claims integrity, and maintain trust in a rapidly evolving digital environment.</p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$49.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>60 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><section class=\"star-bar__container u-margin-top container--max-width\"><div class=\"alert-message u-padding-hug-left u-bg-accent-lavender u-font-family-primary\"><span class=\"u-margin-right u-bg-alert-blue\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-color-white\" height=\"24\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"24\"><use xlink:href=\"#star\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use></svg></span><p>*Enjoy Every Webinar Free with CEU Unlimited  —  <a href=\"#unlimited\">See Below</a> to learn more.<br/>No discount code or pre-paid agreement needed. No hidden or state reporting fees.</p></div></section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div> <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--highlight-bar paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div class=\"u-margin-top u-margin-lg-bottom highlight-bar__container highlight-bar__container--navy\">\n<div class=\"container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--centered container__grid--max-md\">\n<div class=\"highlight-bar__inner\">\n<div class=\"highlight-bar__msg u-text-center\">\n<h2>Webinar Details</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"webinar-content\"><h4>AI Fraud in Focus: Detecting and Defending Against Digital Deception in Insurance</h4><p>Discover how AI is revolutionizing insurance fraud. Learn tactics fraudsters use, red flags to watch for, and strategies to detect, prevent, and mitigate emerging digital threats.</p><h4>Topics</h4><ul><li>Examine how generative AI is used to create fraudulent claims, documents, and synthetic identities</li><li>Identify red flags in claims, media files, and metadata that signal potential fraud</li><li>Understand the impact of AI-enabled scams on underwriting, claims, and internal risk controls</li><li>Build effective prevention strategies using detection tools, audits, and AI-based countermeasures</li><li>Explore regulatory developments and compliance measures to stay ahead of evolving fraud tactics</li></ul></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph